# ===============================
# REST Client for Products API
# ===============================

@productId =2528a332-ca88-4c07-bec9-4f62696295c6

### 1️⃣ Add Product
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Apple",
  "type": "crop",
  "unit": "kg",
  "description": "Fresh apples",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/apple.jpg"
}

###

### 2️⃣ Get All Products
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products
Accept: application/json

###

### 2️⃣ Get All Products with Type Filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?type=crop
Accept: application/json

###

### 2️⃣ Get All Products with Name Search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?name=apple
Accept: application/json

###

### 3️⃣ Get Product Details by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 4️⃣ Update Product
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Green Apple",
  "unit": "kg",
  "description": "Fresh green apples"
}

###

### 5️⃣ Delete Product
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json
